Cistron Biotechnology Inc saidit will pay a stock dividend declared prior to the initialpublic offering of its common stock in August 1986 tostockholders of record prior to the common offering.    Payment of the dividend was contingent on the closing bidprice of the common stock averaging two dlrs or more per sharesfor the trading days within any consecutive ten day periodending before February 29, 1988. The company said that thecontingency has been fulfilled.    Payment of the stock dividend increases Cistron'soutstanding common stock to 21,390,190 shares from 16,185,354shares. Reuter&#3;